high_descs: Stand in front of the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the mug on the left. Close the door. Turn microwave on for six seconds. Open the door. Take out the mug. Close the door.
Go forward, cross to the left, then to the right and stand in front of the dresser next to the bed.
Place the mug on the left side of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Place the mug on the left side of the dresser.

high_descs: Enter the kitchen and face the countertop to the right of the sink.
Pick up the mug from the counter.
Turn around to reach the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave and take it out.
Head to the passage on the right and turn left to walk to the end of the passage and hang right to enter the bedroom and reach the dresser on the left of the bed.
Put the cup on the left of the other mug on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mug on the dresser.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the counter top.
Take the mug from the counter top.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the mug into the microwave.
Turn around and go near the dresser.
Put the mug on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Placed the mug on the dresser.
